Packages that use breakout
Package
Description
breakout
Contains types that define the brick-breaking game object model.

Contains types that define the Command Design Pattern for use with the brick-breaking application.
breakout.application.windows
Contains types that define the brick-breaking application for window-based operating systems.
breakout.application.windows.state
Contains types that define the State Design Pattern for use with the brick-breaking application for window-based operating systems.
